{"title":"你好 Hexo","slug":"你好 Hexo","date":"2023-06-08T07:01:00.000Z","updated":"2023-10-30T06:11:42.233Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/你好 Hexo.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"开始hexohexo使用文档<br>https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/","covers":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"开始hexo\"><a href=\"#开始hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开始hexo\"></a>开始hexo</h1><p>hexo使用文档<br><a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/\">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</a></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p>b站视频教程<br><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1q741167PJ/?p=4&spm_id_from=pageDriver&vd_source=e55fc0a4191bb84a11c6fbacf9e809c7\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1q741167PJ/?p=4&amp;spm_id_from=pageDriver&amp;vd_source=e55fc0a4191bb84a11c6fbacf9e809c7</a></p>\n<p>全局安装</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>开始构建</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 创建</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init blog</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 进入目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd blog</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 安装环境</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br><span class=\"line\">启动</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>下载主题<br><a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git clone https://github.com/HeskeyBaozi/hexo-theme-lite.git themes/hexo-theme-lite</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h1 id=\"写作\"><a href=\"#写作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"写作\"></a>写作</h1><p>创建文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>layout布局<br>post：这是默认的布局，适用于普通的博客文章。<br>page：适用于创建页面，比如关于我、联系我等等。<br>category：适用于按分类组织的博客文章。<br>tag：适用于按标签组织的博客文章。<br>draft：适用于草稿文章，还没有发布。</p>\n<p>markdown文件头设置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">--- title: 脚本参数化的思考</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: 2019-01-01 11:20:32</span><br><span class=\"line\">tags: [标签1,标签2]</span><br><span class=\"line\">categories: 分类</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}